0:02:24.000,0:02:27.700
Your Majesty stayed up late with Lady Shen last night.

0:02:27.875,0:02:29.400
Why didn't Your Majesty sleep in for a bit?

0:02:29.400,0:02:32.795
All the joy aside,
I have to hold court in the morning.

0:02:32.795,0:02:35.000
You didn't sleep well either, did you?

0:02:35.500,0:02:37.000
For one thing, I was overjoyed;

0:02:37.000,0:02:41.000
for another, I must ensure the the Imperial Infirmary
is able to take care of Lady Shen.

0:02:41.720,0:02:43.180
Your hard work is appreciated.

0:02:45.440,0:02:46.860
Noble Lady Shen ...

0:02:47.260,0:02:49.040
What about her, Your Majesty?

0:02:51.280,0:02:54.100
I wish to promote Noble Lady Shen.

0:02:55.000,0:02:57.565
Your Majesty is very fond of Lady Shen,
and now she is with child.

0:02:57.565,0:03:00.200
Her promotion is reasonably expected.

0:03:00.200,0:03:05.000
However, there is no precedent for a concubine
to be promoted upon conception or delivery.

0:03:06.000,0:03:08.455
It's not entirely because of her pregnancy.

0:03:08.815,0:03:10.800
Her stable personality is a rarity.

0:03:10.800,0:03:12.445
That is true.

0:03:12.445,0:03:15.285
Compared to Lady Sourire's keen intellect,

0:03:15.285,0:03:17.500
Lady Shen is responsible and decorous.

0:03:17.800,0:03:20.305
Does Your Majesty intend to promote
Lady Shen to Concubine?

0:03:21.125,0:03:23.300
- She's worthy of the title.
- Absolutely.

0:03:23.500,0:03:27.195
In this way, however, there will be two concubines
as the heads of the Palace of Universal Happiness.

0:03:27.500,0:03:32.000
I'm afraid it will be inconvenient for Lady Shen
to move to another palace in her pregnancy.

0:03:32.155,0:03:36.500
Why don't we double her happiness
when her child is born?

0:03:38.000,0:03:40.780
You're right.

0:03:40.780,0:03:43.600
But I feel obliged to reward her.

0:03:44.625,0:03:47.055
Jewelry is all too trivial.

0:03:47.780,0:03:51.360
Since her promotion is temporarily delayed,
I wish to give her an honorary name in advance.

0:03:52.040,0:03:54.340
Your Majesty must have a name in mind already.

0:03:54.500,0:03:59.520
I'm thinking of naming her Vertu [惠Hui].

0:03:59.520,0:04:03.000
Hmm, that perfectly describes her.

0:04:05.435,0:04:09.625
Lady Sourire and Lady Shen are like sisters.

0:04:09.625,0:04:11.665
Now they're finally equal.

0:04:18.500,0:04:21.500
What a joyous occasion that your wish came true!

0:04:21.500,0:04:23.180
I don't see the joy of that.

0:04:23.180,0:04:26.120
All of a sudden I'm restricted to do this and that.

0:04:26.120,0:04:27.780
It's such a bore!

0:04:27.780,0:04:29.200
There's still nine months to come.

0:04:29.200,0:04:30.780
But the time will fly by.

0:04:30.780,0:04:34.000
Jinxi said that you will reunite with your family
in the 8th month of your pregnancy.

0:04:34.000,0:04:38.800
Your mother will enter the palace to take care of you.

0:04:38.960,0:04:41.440
For real? That'll be great!

0:04:44.500,0:04:46.900
I’ve set my sights on  the baby in your belly.

0:04:46.900,0:04:48.780
When will I be his honorary mother?
[similar to the role of a godmother but non-religious]

0:04:49.280,0:04:51.460
What use are you as an honorary mother?

0:04:51.460,0:04:53.660
You'll be a mother soon as well.

0:04:53.800,0:04:57.200
We don't even know yet whether it's a boy or a girl.

0:04:57.360,0:04:59.240
I'll take anything!

0:04:59.240,0:05:04.420
I wish it is a prince, upon whom
I can rely on for the rest of my life.

0:05:04.920,0:05:09.720
For the place you hold in His Majesty's heart,
he will love a girl just as much as a boy.

0:05:10.920,0:05:14.520
I'm afraid you'll be promoted again while you're still sitting the month [postpartum confinement].

0:05:14.520,0:05:16.560
Don't make fun of me.

0:05:16.800,0:05:22.400
I was going to tell you something important,
which I remembered when I woke up this morning.

0:05:22.400,0:05:25.180
What could possibly be
more important than your pregnancy?

0:05:25.400,0:05:26.860
This is a serious matter.

0:05:26.860,0:05:30.820
Consort Fleur might get back on her feet.

0:05:30.820,0:05:33.740
I'm afraid that you won't
be able to deal with her on your own.

0:05:33.740,0:05:39.720
Honestly, I do not expect His Majesty
to devote himself to just one woman.

0:05:40.960,0:05:44.360
Someone might take advantage of
the vacuum during my pregnancy.

0:05:45.720,0:05:49.600
Are you suggesting ... that we bring Lingrong here?

0:05:50.000,0:05:51.080
Exactly.

0:05:51.080,0:05:52.740
Look at you!

0:05:52.740,0:05:56.100
You were the one who called her ruthless.
Now you wish she was here.

0:05:56.100,0:05:59.000
Well, being ruthless has its own benefits.

0:05:59.280,0:06:01.780
We need to plan ahead for you.

0:06:01.780,0:06:06.940
We won't be out of our wits
in event of a crisis if she's with us.

0:06:08.000,0:06:10.660
I will make a request to His Majesty
at his earliest convenience.

0:06:10.660,0:06:13.740
I don't believe he would refuse.

0:06:14.200,0:06:19.100
He'll give anything to his number-one concubine.

0:06:20.040,0:06:23.380
But you must not worry yourself over anything.

0:06:23.380,0:06:25.500
Your health is our top priority.

0:06:25.800,0:06:28.040
You're right.

0:06:44.460,0:06:45.720
Sourire!

0:06:47.260,0:06:49.100
You've finally arrived.

0:06:58.400,0:07:00.680
- How was the trip?
- It was all right.

0:07:01.600,0:07:04.520
You shouldn't have waited for me outside.

0:07:04.520,0:07:07.380
It's such a hot day.
I hope you are not drenched in sweat.

0:07:09.240,0:07:12.400
I was permitted to come here at Meizhuang's bidding.

0:07:12.400,0:07:13.820
How is she?

0:07:14.000,0:07:15.000
Everything's fine with her.

0:07:15.000,0:07:17.780
She's even happier now that you're here.

0:07:19.120,0:07:25.500
The eunuchs were saying that
His Majesty indulges all of Meizhuang's desires.

0:07:26.640,0:07:29.920
"Seeing is believing."
You'll see for yourself.

0:07:31.460,0:07:33.800
But before that, we shall pay respect to His Majesty.

0:07:34.700,0:07:36.500
Yes, certainly.

0:07:45.000,0:07:48.080
Prince, you've been waiting here for half a day.

0:07:48.080,0:07:51.100
You might get sun stroke if you stay here.

0:07:52.500,0:07:54.060
Mr Su.

0:07:54.300,0:07:57.580
Peace to Lady Sourire.
Peace to Companion An.

0:07:58.480,0:08:01.020
Mr Su, who is the kid?

0:08:02.000,0:08:05.000
That is the Fourth Prince.
He wishes to see His Majesty.

0:08:05.400,0:08:06.620
The Fourth Prince?

0:08:06.700,0:08:08.480
I've never heard of him.

0:08:08.480,0:08:11.040
He's been living in the Summer Palace.

0:08:11.040,0:08:13.440
Does His Majesty not have time to see the Fourth Prince?

0:08:14.500,0:08:18.520
I'm afraid His Majesty is not in the mood to see anyone.

0:08:18.800,0:08:20.780
My Ladies, you may come at another time.

0:08:20.780,0:08:24.000
Sourire, shall we ...

0:08:24.220,0:08:26.800
shall we go back for now?

0:08:28.000,0:08:30.000
What a poor kid!

0:08:30.000,0:08:35.000
Sir, may I trouble you to send the Fourth Prince
lotus seed soup to relieve summer heat?

0:08:35.900,0:08:37.300
I will, My Lady.

0:08:42.240,0:08:45.300
Now that you're here, the quiet garden will be livelier.

0:08:45.460,0:08:48.540
I would not be able to come were it not for you two.

0:08:48.540,0:08:50.600
Has Consort Fleur mended her fences with His Majesty?

0:08:50.600,0:08:53.160
She lives away from His Majesty's residence.
They don't get to see each other a lot.

0:08:53.440,0:08:56.040
Peace to My Ladies.

0:08:56.980,0:08:58.640
I bow in respect before Lady Sourire.

0:08:58.640,0:09:01.000
Peace and grace to Your Highness.
[The prince addresses her this way to show respect.]

0:09:01.560,0:09:03.560
Madam Zhang, this is Lady Sourire.

0:09:04.000,0:09:05.300
My Lady.

0:09:05.300,0:09:06.960
Please rise, Fourth Prince.

0:09:07.000,0:09:10.580
We've never met before.
How did you know who I am?

0:09:10.580,0:09:16.200
I saw Your Highness outside the Governance Hall.
I felt that you are an amiable person even by a distant glimpse.

0:09:16.200,0:09:17.840
That is how I met Your Highness.

0:09:17.840,0:09:20.280
And Your Highness met me as well.

0:09:20.280,0:09:24.400
Likewise, I share the same sentiment.

0:09:24.400,0:09:26.000
It was a great pleasure to meet Your Highness.

0:09:26.420,0:09:27.980
Thank you.

0:09:28.000,0:09:29.860
This is Companion An.

0:09:29.860,0:09:31.800
Peace to Your Highness.

0:09:32.520,0:09:34.440
My Pleasure.

0:09:38.880,0:09:42.000
Lingrong, how about you go check on your residence?

0:09:42.100,0:09:44.300
I will go with you to visit Meizhuang later.

0:09:47.080,0:09:48.780
I shall take my leave.

0:09:49.000,0:09:51.580
- Vermilion, please go with her.
- Yes.

0:09:58.000,0:10:01.760
Madam Zhang, I wish to have a word with Lady Sourire.
Can you stand aside?

0:10:09.140,0:10:11.900
Madam Zhang seems to care a lot for you.

0:10:11.900,0:10:14.900
What would you like to say to me
that she can't even listen to?

0:10:16.500,0:10:18.120
I hope Your Highness will forgive my intruding,

0:10:18.120,0:10:23.400
but I thought you could answer my question
for you know Father the best as his favorite concubine.

0:10:23.400,0:10:26.280
Your Highness, I simply wish to know ...

0:10:26.280,0:10:29.600
Is it true that father dislikes me.

0:10:31.320,0:10:34.740
Why would you think that way?
Your Father is just too busy.

0:10:34.740,0:10:39.300
But why has he been keeping me here
for all these years and never visits me?

0:10:39.500,0:10:44.140
And he never allows me to pay respect to him
to fulfill my filial piety?

0:10:45.240,0:10:48.700
His Majesty is busy administering
all things under heaven.

0:10:48.700,0:10:53.380
While you've been living here and rarely seen His Majesty,

0:10:53.380,0:10:56.780
he cares about you no less than the Fifth Prince.

0:10:56.780,0:11:00.600
The Fifth Prince has been living outside the palace as well.

0:11:00.780,0:11:03.820
But the Fifth Prince has a mother.

0:11:03.820,0:11:07.360
My mother was disdained for her humble background.

0:11:08.620,0:11:10.660
A person's value comes from within himself.

0:11:10.660,0:11:13.920
Although I know nothing about your mother,

0:11:13.920,0:11:17.580
I'm sure she loves you
as much as every mother loves their child.

0:11:17.580,0:11:23.620
It doesn't matter what people think about you.
It's what you think of yourself that counts!

0:11:23.620,0:11:27.000
In days to come, they will not dare to
have the least contempt for you.

0:11:27.120,0:11:28.600
For real?

0:11:28.880,0:11:33.700
You wouldn't have come to ask me if you didn't trust me.

0:11:33.760,0:11:35.920
I appreciate Your Highness's advice!

0:11:35.920,0:11:42.260
But I wonder why you would trust me the first time we meet.

0:11:42.260,0:11:46.000
I believe that a concubine does not win
Father's affection with nothing.

0:11:46.000,0:11:49.940
And Your Highness is not even afraid of Consort Fleur.

0:11:50.200,0:11:53.000
I admire you as a person possessing bravery and brains.

0:11:53.200,0:11:57.300
I do not deserve your flattery.

0:11:58.260,0:12:01.240
I wish you will remember that

0:12:01.240,0:12:05.760
instead of admiring a person, become them.

0:12:06.000,0:12:08.500
Is Father really very busy?

0:12:08.880,0:12:12.000
If so, I will administer the country for him when I grow up.

0:12:12.200,0:12:12.960
Aiya,

0:12:12.960,0:12:14.540
you must not say such things.

0:12:19.300,0:12:22.720
- Would you like some snacks?
- For sure!

0:12:32.320,0:12:34.000
Jiuzhou Qingyan
(The Peaceful Nine States)

0:12:47.920,0:12:51.340
I really like this place!
It's so nice and cool in here.

0:12:51.340,0:12:55.720
And the music from the lake
can be best appreciated in here.

0:12:59.640,0:13:05.180
The palace rules only allow the highly ranked noblemen
to visit the concubines on important occasions.

0:13:05.180,0:13:07.480
I do not recognize any of the lords and ladies.

0:13:07.480,0:13:09.360
Do you know who they are?

0:13:10.200,0:13:13.200
That is Lord V,  State Prince Heng,
with his Prince Consort [secondary wife].

0:13:13.200,0:13:15.000
State Prince Heng [prince of the first rank]

0:13:21.540,0:13:25.440
The first one from left looks very dignified.
He inspires awe in me.

0:13:29.660,0:13:33.040
But he seems very nice to his wife.

0:13:33.040,0:13:35.060
(State Prince Dun)

0:13:35.060,0:13:38.940
That is Lord X, whose mother was the younger sister
of the empress of the prior emperor.

0:13:38.940,0:13:42.020
That is why he has an air of authority.

0:13:43.800,0:13:48.040
However, the prior emperor wasn't very fond of
Lord X for his notorious short temper.

0:13:48.040,0:13:50.640
But Lord X is extremely nice to his wife.

0:13:50.640,0:13:54.160
They say a real man is defined by his power,

0:13:54.160,0:13:57.820
but in my eyes, a real man is defined by his love for his family.

0:14:04.300,0:14:08.700
Yun-e, I'd like to make a toast
to you and your wife.

0:14:11.340,0:14:13.120
I thank Your Majesty.

0:14:27.700,0:14:32.640
Sourire, State Prince Dun seems
disrespectful to His Majesty.

0:14:32.800,0:14:35.340
Why is His Majesty so respectful to him?

0:14:36.400,0:14:42.120
After the battle for the throne among the nine princes,
His Majesty has to stabilize the government.

0:14:52.000,0:14:57.040
I wonder what's keeping Yunli this time.
He still hasn't appeared.

0:14:57.100,0:14:59.160
Your Majesty knows how he is.

0:14:59.160,0:15:02.200
( Venerable Prince Shen [prince of the third rank] )
He follows no rule.

0:15:02.500,0:15:07.860
A family banquet isn't a big deal after all.
I'll let him be.

0:15:10.400,0:15:15.240
Lady Vertu, that is a very nice hairpin you're wearing.

0:15:15.600,0:15:18.080
Is it the new gift from the Empress Dowager?

0:15:18.080,0:15:19.300
Yes.

0:15:19.300,0:15:23.620
The Empress Dowager specially had the hairpin sent here to congratulate Lady Vertu on her pregnancy.

0:15:23.800,0:15:30.040
The Two Gods of Harmony on the hairpin will
bless her with plentiful children and good fortune.

0:15:31.300,0:15:35.560
This is a special gift because the Empress Dowager
received it when she was pregnant with Lord XIV.

0:15:35.700,0:15:40.320
On that account, we can see how much the Empress Dowager is looking forward to Lady Vertu's child.

0:15:40.700,0:15:44.880
I can't wait to see what a cute prince it will be.

0:15:46.000,0:15:47.300
It's not necessarily a prince.

0:15:47.300,0:15:50.400
I'm hoping that it is a princess as adorable as Wenyi.

0:15:53.000,0:15:55.240
Enjoy.

0:16:01.560,0:16:05.400
(Consort Honnête)

0:16:17.280,0:16:20.200
Her Highness Consort Honnête.

0:16:22.240,0:16:25.820
Her Highness Consort Honnête.

0:16:39.160,0:16:43.420
May peace and grace be with Your Majesties.

0:16:43.600,0:16:44.500
Rise.

0:16:44.600,0:16:46.580
I thank Your Majesty.

0:16:59.680,0:17:02.440
Your Majesty has obtained 
reminiscence (in a new concubine).

0:17:02.940,0:17:09.760
You've kept the same eye for all these years.

0:17:09.760,0:17:12.860
You shouldn't have come on such a scorching day.

0:17:13.000,0:17:16.860
We're just having a meal.
It's nothing significant.

0:17:17.820,0:17:21.520
This is a joyous occasion for Wenyi.
I must come to celebrate for her.

0:17:21.520,0:17:24.740
I haven't seen her for a long time.

0:17:25.000,0:17:27.780
- Take your seat.
- I thank Your Majesty.

0:17:28.760,0:17:32.160
Wenyi was just one month old when I last saw her.

0:17:32.820,0:17:35.700
Bring Wenyi to greet Her Highness quickly.

0:17:42.420,0:17:45.500
I would really like to hold her in my arms.

0:17:45.500,0:17:49.360
But I don't have the strength to.

0:17:50.960,0:17:52.680
Auspice.

0:18:02.800,0:18:05.220
The choker was part of your dowries.

0:18:05.800,0:18:10.020
Why would you give such a valuable gift to a small child?

0:18:10.760,0:18:12.780
Your Majesty has a good memory.

0:18:12.900,0:18:18.980
Considering my persisting health condition,
it will come of no use if I keep it.

0:18:19.660,0:18:23.060
It is a perfect gift for the adorable princess.

0:18:24.820,0:18:27.580
I thank Your Highness on behalf of Wenyi.

0:18:27.600,0:18:29.180
My pleasure.

